data.meta_description: The homepage of flautist Philippa Davies. Information on concerts, CD's, biography, pictures and more.
data.text:
Welcome to the homepage of Philippa Davies.

To be released soon:

A Celebration of Paul Reade

A new album celebrating the music of Paul Reade â creator of much-loved TV theme tunes including Antiques Roadshow

Digital release: 17th March

CD release: 18th August

Paul Reade, who died in 1997, would have been 80 this year. The new album - which is the result of a crowdfunder campaign I initiated - serves to honour the occasion by creating a lasting legacy of his much-loved work. Entitled A Celebration of Paul Reade, the album features not only the suite from The Victorian Kitchen Garden but also Readeâs Chants du Roussillon and world premiere recordings of four other works.
